graph TD
    Start[Code Implementation] --> Build{Build Success?}
    
    Build -- No --> FixBuild[Fix Compilation Errors]
    FixBuild --> Build
    
    Build -- Yes --> TestUnit{Unit Tests Pass?}
    TestUnit -- No --> FixTests[Fix Logic or Test]
    FixTests --> TestUnit
    
    TestUnit -- Yes --> Coverage{Coverage >= 95%?}
    Coverage -- No --> AddTests[Add More Test Cases]
    AddTests --> TestUnit
    
    Coverage -- Yes --> RunApp{App Runtime Check}
    RunApp -- Fail --> DebugRun[Debug Startup Crash]
    DebugRun --> RunApp
    
    RunApp -- Success --> Postman[Generate Postman Collection]
    Postman --> VerifyCurl{Verify Endpoint with Curl}
    VerifyCurl -- Fail --> FixEndpoint[Fix Controller/DTO]
    FixEndpoint --> TestUnit
    
    VerifyCurl -- Success --> Done[Ready for Delivery]
